Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.15,0:00:00.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.30,0:01:45.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.52,0:01:46.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小優…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.02,0:01:48.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.42,0:01:52.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點施加詛咒把他殺了 優
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.35,0:01:54.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.46,0:01:57.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.00,0:01:59.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.13,0:02:17.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.41,0:02:19.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這傢伙為什麼沒殺了他
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.86,0:02:21.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.44,0:02:27.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.44,0:02:30.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別擔這種無謂的心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.28,0:02:33.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我看著前面 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.32,0:02:34.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡可是戰場
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.04,0:02:37.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋優 你在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.21,0:02:39.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才絕對能殺了他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.56,0:02:42.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼沒有發動鬼咒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.77,0:02:44.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,優君 你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.65,0:02:49.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,優…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.64,0:02:51.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米迦…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.32,0:02:54.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的家人…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.88,0:02:59.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在吸血鬼裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.73,0:03:05.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你是米迦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.66,0:03:15.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米迦…米迦…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.50,0:03:20.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是米迦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.82,0:03:23.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小優…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.61,0:03:29.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 那個可愛的態度是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.69,0:03:32.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,念念不忘的百夜優一郎君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.50,0:03:34.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一直想要見的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.05,0:03:37.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過沒想到會命運般地重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.86,0:03:40.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼淚都快掉下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.97,0:03:42.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼你打算怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.81,0:03:46.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,估計小優在被人類利用喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.35,0:03:48.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然要救他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.16,0:03:50.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從醜陋的人類手裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.88,0:03:51.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.14,0:03:54.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是他也是人類喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.74,0:03:57.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類是絕不可能成為我們的同伴的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.94,0:04:04.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 有了 就像克魯魯對你做的那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.57,0:04:08.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來把小優變成吸血鬼吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.25,0:04:15.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是敢對小優出手就宰了你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.94,0:04:17.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.13,0:04:20.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然變得那麼火爆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.49,0:04:24.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼讓我助你一臂之力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.91,0:04:28.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他的人類由我來解決
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.88,0:04:34.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去把你最珍視的公主大人給奪過來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.64,0:04:39.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小優 找到同伴了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.84,0:04:40.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟你那麼溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.87,0:04:43.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過正因為如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.64,0:04:46.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因為你過於溫柔才會被欺騙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.22,0:04:51.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類…戴著同伴假面具的他們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.28,0:04:53.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是極其貪婪的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.13,0:04:54.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小優…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.53,0:05:08.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 動手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.39,0:05:12.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把小優以外的人類全部殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.13,0:05:15.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說您找我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.30,0:05:17.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第七位始祖大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.21,0:05:20.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是克勞利君嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.71,0:05:21.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等你好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.50,0:05:23.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.14,0:05:26.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我稍微去別處逛了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.46,0:05:29.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發現什麼有趣的東西了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.18,0:05:29.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.80,0:05:34.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過你們來了的話 他們也就玩完了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.03,0:05:37.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 把他們變成家畜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.64,0:05:42.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生擒起來 名為吸血鬼殲滅部隊家畜化計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.89,0:05:44.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不錯的提議
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.64,0:05:47.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 貴族又增加了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.94,0:05:48.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.10,0:05:52.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全員撤退準備
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.04,0:05:57.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 那邊有米迦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.94,0:05:59.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有我的家人在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.78,0:06:01.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…所以別撤退…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.67,0:06:04.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼你想在這裡全軍覆沒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.10,0:06:06.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,優君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.68,0:06:12.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,優…現在就先…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.98,0:06:20.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撤退了 保持陣型後退至第二防禦線
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.85,0:06:28.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會讓你們逃走的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.59,0:06:29.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,散開
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.42,0:06:30.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs37\an8}是你！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.15,0:06:37.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼啊 優
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.79,0:06:39.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你 是你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.25,0:06:49.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,優
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.18,0:06:50.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.77,0:06:52.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中校
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.43,0:06:58.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好快 不過還太嫩了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.89,0:07:10.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後 就算是獅子受傷之後劍也變遲鈍了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.26,0:07:14.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅蓮大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.83,0:07:22.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.80,0:07:28.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 站住
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.37,0:07:36.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸 真不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.77,0:07:38.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還會露出這種表情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.59,0:07:42.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美十
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.94,0:07:44.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.37,0:07:48.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來對方無論如何都不會讓我們過去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.77,0:07:50.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有先解決掉才行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.76,0:07:52.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說得簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.62,0:07:55.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能做到的話就不會這麼辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.00,0:07:59.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放棄吧 你們只有成為家畜一條路
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.80,0:08:02.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.64,0:08:19.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,集中精神
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.46,0:08:25.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼 快點站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.34,0:08:26.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.48,0:08:28.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又見面了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.31,0:08:36.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次可不會放過你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.52,0:08:41.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.73,0:08:47.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,背後
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.02,0:08:53.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先從你的血開始嘗…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.19,0:09:05.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別那麼生氣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.55,0:09:09.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過是個可愛的玩笑而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.17,0:09:11.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米迦…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.09,0:09:19.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小優 拋棄這裡的一切和我一起逃走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.07,0:09:22.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 逃走是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.81,0:09:26.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說 你為什麼會和那個吸血鬼在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.15,0:09:26.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別多說了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.91,0:09:31.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,優
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.41,0:09:35.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,東張西望可不行喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.21,0:09:42.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 開什麼玩笑米迦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.86,0:09:44.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟是怎麼回事給我說明一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.36,0:09:47.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小優不能繼續待在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.58,0:09:49.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會被人類利用的 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.28,0:09:52.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 快點停下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.84,0:09:54.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我適可而止一點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.65,0:10:00.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被人類利用？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.13,0:10:02.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.98,0:10:03.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.44,0:10:20.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已經不是人類了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.91,0:10:22.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因為我的錯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.54,0:10:24.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.64,0:10:27.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的 不是小優的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.22,0:10:29.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.85,0:10:30.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別說了 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.55,0:10:33.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡太危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.98,0:10:39.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小優 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.54,0:10:43.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做不到 米迦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.37,0:10:46.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能走 我的同伴…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.61,0:10:49.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你錯了 那不是你的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.51,0:10:51.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別被騙了 小優
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.56,0:10:53.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類是在利用你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.84,0:10:55.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,筱婭同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.30,0:11:04.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,筱婭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.86,0:11:08.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了小優 不要回頭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.90,0:11:09.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你身後什麼都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.53,0:11:11.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.88,0:11:17.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我放手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.87,0:11:21.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小優！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.10,0:11:26.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放開
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.12,0:11:29.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能過去 小優
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.05,0:11:30.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.20,0:11:32.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能過去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.61,0:11:36.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們只是想要利用你而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.52,0:11:39.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.26,0:11:41.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.13,0:11:44.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我一起走吧 小優
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.09,0:11:50.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.96,0:11:57.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,優…快逃…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.46,0:12:00.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家畜別隨便說話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.51,0:12:02.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手…快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.04,0:12:05.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經太遲了 小優 放棄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.40,0:12:31.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小優…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.03,0:13:01.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 阿朱羅丸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.83,0:13:03.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？ 什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.34,0:13:05.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.75,0:13:08.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算奪取我的身體嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.57,0:13:12.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的 我什麼都沒做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.75,0:13:15.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過這可真讓人頭疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.32,0:13:22.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到我竟會對附身之人的怪物形態感到害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.91,0:13:25.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看那片天空
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.41,0:13:30.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彷彿要照亮這個被詛咒的世界一般 蒼穹已開始打開
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.99,0:13:33.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 優 就像米迦說的那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.54,0:13:38.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果還來得及的話 兩個人一起逃離人類會比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.44,0:13:44.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然的話…你將變得不再是人類…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.75,0:13:46.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.51,0:14:02.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎為時已晚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.31,0:14:13.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你非人類的部分開始暴走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.86,0:14:35.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.60,0:14:48.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然人類把小優給…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.24,0:14:53.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 小優 和我一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.40,0:15:27.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出現了個有點棘手的東西啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.97,0:15:49.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這真是厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.02,0:16:05.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小優
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.35,0:16:10.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衣服都弄髒了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.17,0:16:57.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.55,0:17:00.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類不要造這種令人恐怖的怪物好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.54,0:17:02.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦 費里德君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.23,0:17:03.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.96,0:17:06.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.61,0:17:10.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.77,0:17:18.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該是你們人類擅長的人體實驗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.79,0:17:22.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們那永無止盡的慾望到底是從哪湧出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.12,0:17:32.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說實話真有點嚇人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.95,0:17:37.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,況且你們還總是無法控制這些東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.37,0:17:38.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.03,0:17:48.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罪人…罪人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.11,0:17:51.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部都要殺死…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.37,0:17:56.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,筱婭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.34,0:17:58.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你快想點辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.12,0:18:01.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在的優還是能恢復正常的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.34,0:18:29.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 小優
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.35,0:18:31.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以殺人…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.01,0:18:38.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.54,0:18:40.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,閉嘴 人類
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.73,0:18:44.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然利用小優
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.79,0:18:47.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.25,0:18:49.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傷口無法癒合
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.76,0:18:53.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都給我去死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.99,0:18:59.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,筱婭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.64,0:19:02.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快一點 再下去全都會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.87,0:19:04.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,筱婭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.28,0:19:18.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,優 求你了 快清醒過來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.60,0:19:22.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別用你那骯髒的手碰小優
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.22,0:19:23.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,優
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.32,0:19:35.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你了 優
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.14,0:19:41.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,優！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.71,0:20:00.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,優 優
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.02,0:20:08.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,優…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.61,0:20:10.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋人類…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.97,0:20:14.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋人類
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.48,0:20:19.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很華麗的演出吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.63,0:20:21.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可是我的王牌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.15,0:20:24.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 不是什麼結果都沒有出來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.02,0:20:26.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 有結果了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.74,0:20:30.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我們只不過是拖延時間的誘餌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.71,0:20:40.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊呀 暴露了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.95,0:20:42.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 已經遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.49,0:20:46.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把敵人貫穿 「白虎丸」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.10,0:20:49.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 不要打到紅蓮喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.23,0:20:50.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,砰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.27,0:20:56.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.47,0:21:04.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真險 真險
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.60,0:21:09.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果沒有他的忠告 可能已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.00,0:21:21.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這下可真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.79,0:21:26.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為分家的垃圾算做得不錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.53,0:21:27.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一瀨中校
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.97,0:21:32.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來由我們柊家處理
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.74,0:21:36.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上吧 把貴族都給我活捉了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.08,0:21:44.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,違抗人類 日本帝鬼軍 我們柊家的人會有何下場
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.27,0:21:48.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有必要讓他們銘心刻骨地記住
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.69,0:21:51.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,動手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.58,0:23:34.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.47,0:23:35.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終結的熾天使
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.71,0:23:39.55,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(870,0)\frz270\fs75\pos(1146.019,336)}全 都   是 罪 人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.71,0:23:39.55,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\c&HCCF2F4&\pos(1146.019,336)\frz270\fs75\fad(870,0)}全 都   是 罪 人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.71,0:23:35.63,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1a&H9f\blur13\frz270\fs75\pos(1146.019,336)\fad(0,870)}全 都   是 罪 人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.15,0:00:00.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:00:00.15,0:00:00.15,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,=================OPE=================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.44,0:00:14.43,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}I don't want nobody to get killed
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.73,0:00:19.09,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}I'll come and get you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.11,0:00:22.19,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}I am always ready to fight
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.44,0:00:28.17,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}So don't take all of the blame we were all swept away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.23,0:00:32.02,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}Don't take all of the weight. You always do
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.13,0:00:35.72,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}There will always be something you cannot control
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.79,0:00:40.26,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}We will overcome. Your salvation has begun
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.76,0:00:46.05,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}No signs, no lights, such a mess all over
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.14,0:00:48.23,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}Don't kill you hopes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.38,0:00:54.18,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}You make me realize who I need
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.21,0:00:56.57,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}I'll be there hold on
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.71,0:00:58.55,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}They'll change you somehow
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.64,0:01:01.81,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}So where are you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.00,0:01:04.36,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}I'll reach you by dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.38,0:01:09.53,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}The shadows appear，Illusions are born
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.30,0:01:13.50,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}The fallen angels you run with don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.62,0:01:18.11,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}It is our pain that makes us all human after all
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.13,0:01:21.06,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}Torn old sepia photographs show
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.11,0:01:22.92,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}Our fragile precious world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.04,0:01:26.68,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}Must discard it, respond to the call
Comment: 0,0:00:00.15,0:00:00.15,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,=================OPC=================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.44,0:00:14.43,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}我不願意看到有人被殺
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.73,0:00:19.09,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}我將來找尋你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.11,0:00:22.19,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}我一直準備與它們抗爭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.44,0:00:28.17,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}所以別一個人承擔過錯 我們都在命運的洪流中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.23,0:00:32.02,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}別一個人把重任扛在肩上 你總會這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.13,0:00:35.72,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}人生不定 總會有些事你無法掌控
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.79,0:00:40.26,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}而我們會克服一切 對你的救濟已經開始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.76,0:00:46.05,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}生命跡象為零 抬頭不見星光 腳下遍地混沌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.14,0:00:48.23,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}然而不要扼殺你的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.38,0:00:54.18,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}你讓我察覺到我心底所求之人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.21,0:00:56.57,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}我會堅持在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.71,0:00:58.55,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}可曾幾何時你已被他們改變
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.64,0:01:01.81,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}而真正的你今在何方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.00,0:01:04.36,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}我會在黎明前找到你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.38,0:01:09.53,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}身影浮現 幻影所生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.30,0:01:13.50,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}你所追逐的 你所不了解的墮落天使們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.62,0:01:18.11,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}畢竟我們的痛苦讓我們更像是人類
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.13,0:01:21.06,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}被撕碎的紅褐色的照片上 所映出的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.11,0:01:22.92,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}是我們脆弱的而又美好的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.04,0:01:26.68,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}必須拋棄舊世界 響應使命的召喚
Comment: 0,0:00:00.15,0:00:00.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,=================EDJ=================
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.47,0:22:17.31,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}馴染めた白　鳥かご隅　鼓動獲たツボミも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.71,0:22:28.45,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}置き去り声　眩めた　記憶の影
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.61,0:22:31.49,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}I need your blood
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.56,0:22:34.24,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}You read love 唱える
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.34,0:22:37.88,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\an1}足掻く　RED LIGHT
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.94,0:22:43.84,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}嗅ぎ分けた音と
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.90,0:22:46.82,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}こじ開けたReasonが
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.98,0:22:50.01,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}ただ平行に並ぶ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.96,0:22:55.66,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}Come and break it down for me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.74,0:22:57.70,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}A river will flow
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.01,0:23:04.00,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}KEYがない「欲しい」でも　利害鳴る鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.25,0:23:14.10,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}懺悔さえ乾いた ４拍子が　奏でた意図を辿る
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.31,0:23:21.25,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}木漏れ日の赤が騒ぐ
Comment: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,=================EDC=================
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.47,0:22:17.31,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}不變的蒼白景色 枷鎖般的鳥籠之內 花蕾獲得了新生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.71,0:22:28.45,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}你漸離漸遠的聲音 是我不敢直視的記憶影子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.56,0:22:34.24,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}高呼 {\fnDFHSMincho-W3\fs25}You read love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.34,0:22:37.88,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\an1}不斷掙扎  {\fnDFHSMincho-W3\fs25}RED LIGHT
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.94,0:22:43.84,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}感應到的聲音和
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.90,0:22:46.82,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}最終揭開的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.98,0:22:50.01,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}永遠只是不相交的平行線
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.01,0:23:04.00,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}無窮無盡的慾望 是鳴響得失的警鈴
